title: #246 Chip Bones
description:
It's a toothy Tuesdays as Joe shepherds Sarah Tollemache around the city to fix her chipped tooth while Mark trips on shrooms all over the city of New Orleans. Plus, Joe may have saved a woman's life! Check it out!

Subscribe to our Patreon for new bonus eps featuring Ron Bennington, Chris Distefano, Nikki Glaser, and Yannas Pappas. Plus, a new bonus vid with Joe, Robert Kelly & Ari Shaffir!
